      "blocks": {
        "story-eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>SINCE 2018</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true
          }
        },
        "story-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Born from a Love of Practice",
            "size": "2xl"
          }
        },
        "story-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Stillpoint began as a simple idea: a studio where the practice comes first. Founded by Sarah Chen after years of teaching in crowded gyms and noisy fitness chains, Stillpoint was designed to be the opposite — a quiet, intentional space where students could reconnect with their bodies and breath.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        },
        "story-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What started as a single room on Willow Street has grown into a community of hundreds of regular practitioners. But the mission hasn't changed: create a space that feels like home, teach with honesty and care, and make yoga accessible to everyone who walks through the door.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["story-eyebrow", "story-heading", "story-text-1", "story-text-2"]
    },
    "values": {
      "type": "features-split",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "What Guides Us",
        "title": "Our Values",
        "description": "",
        "heading_alignment": "center",
        "content_position": "start",
        "show_divider": false,
        "icon_style": "outline",
        "icon_size": "lg",
        "icon_shape": "circle",
        "color_scheme": "standard-secondary"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "value-1": {
          "type": "feature",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "accessible",
            "title": "Accessible to All",
            "description": "<p>Yoga is for every body. We offer modifications in every class, sliding-scale pricing, and a welcoming environment where no one is judged for where they are in their practice.</p>"
          }
        },
        "value-2": {
          "type": "feature",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "leaf",
            "title": "Rooted in Tradition",
            "description": "<p>We honor the ancient roots of yoga while teaching in a way that's relevant and accessible today. Our approach blends classical philosophy with modern anatomy and movement science.</p>"
          }
        },
        "value-3": {
          "type": "feature",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "users",
            "title": "Community First",
            "description": "<p>Stillpoint is more than a studio — it's a gathering place. We host workshops, seasonal events, and community classes because we believe practice is richer when it's shared.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["value-1", "value-2", "value-3"]
    },
